lead_paragraph: Veteran swimmer Ryan Lochte's brush with Rio police has already hurt his appeal to sponsors - but for two lesser-known team mates, it means they may never get a chance to sign their first major deal.

headline.main: #LochteGate Means Lesser-Known Swimmers May Miss Their Pay Day
